Dear [Hiring Manager name],

I am writing to express my keen interest in the [Job Title] position at [Company Name], as advertised on [Website Name]. 
With [Number] years of experience in [Your Field], I have consistently delivered exceptional results in [Specific Achievements].

My expertise in [Skill 1], [Skill 2], and [Skill 3] aligns perfectly with the requirements outlined in your job posting.
I am particularly drawn to your company's focus on [Company Value], and I am eager to contribute my skills and experience to your team.

Thank you for considering my application. I have attached my resume for your review and look forward to the opportunity to discuss how I can contribute to [Company Name]'s continued success.

Sincerely, [Your Name]

Dear Hiring Manager, 
I am excited to apply for [job] with [Company], 
强调你能为公司做什么
突出正确的技能和经验

我是xxx, 目前任職於xx,有5+yrs於智慧製造產業服務的經驗，並之前有3年軟體產品開發的經驗。從linkedin上看到你們有[職位]的需求，我對這個職位非常感興趣，以下是我於各領域的簡單描述，請參閱
[全端開發] 維護開發全廠20+之網頁需求，前端開發有VUEJS, JAVASCRIPT, REACTJS使用經驗，後端也有FLASK, FASTAPI, DJANGO開發經驗
[產品開發] 之前有3+ yrs軟體開發經驗，所開發之能源管理產品目前供TSMC及各大公司使用。產出數千萬元效益
[智慧製造] 有Scikit-learn, Keras, tensorflow使用經驗，參與競賽[]獲取第3名，實際產出效益如下:應用影像辨識技術，減少90%之人工判讀時間。整合並建立資料自動化流程，減少90%人工資料檢索時間

I'm passionate about [Company]'s mission and would love to bring my [add your awesome skills here] to this position.
  
